1471
00:57:37,640 --> 00:57:39,280
Let's be together.

1472
00:57:39,280 --> 00:57:40,200
Here, babe.

1473
00:57:41,280 --> 00:57:42,480
Thanks, babe.

1474
00:57:42,560 --> 00:57:43,560
Kiss me.

1475
00:57:43,560 --> 00:57:44,480
Kiss you?

1476
00:57:44,480 --> 00:57:45,480
You're serious?

1477
00:57:46,880 --> 00:57:48,680
When we were taking those photos,

1478
00:57:48,680 --> 00:57:50,080
