1480
00:57:53,320 --> 00:57:54,120
I was so moved.

1481
00:57:54,120 --> 00:57:55,040
Really. moved.

1482
00:57:55,760 --> 00:57:56,560
Come closer.

1483
00:57:59,400 --> 00:58:00,400
What's gonna happen tomorrow?

1484
00:58:00,400 --> 00:58:01,600
It depends on you.

1485
