1503
00:58:23,720 --> 00:58:25,120
But every time you go silent like that,

1504
00:58:25,120 --> 00:58:26,640
(Right in the heart)
it hits me right in the heart.

1505
00:58:28,080 --> 00:58:29,200
I think you're

1506
